Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,灰の雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いかん！ありゃ残され雲じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:06.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,すぐに嫁を！嫁をこしらえるんじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:25.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その黒雲に名はなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:29.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,空にただひとつ残されたように浮かぶ姿から、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:33.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,残され雲とだけ呼ばれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ash rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's "Nokosaregumo"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, prepare a bride. Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The black cloud had no proper name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It floated over the land all alone,  \N as if left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So the people often called it \N"Nokosaregumo," the Forsaken Cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, one day my passion's fire will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One day the flames would die out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I didn't need anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But even now, I'm so serious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... but I'm gonna burn it up, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling, it's not that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But surely it's not that bad either
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Party is over
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry darling Hurry up  \N Ah... I still have time to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Light it up, baby.  \N I'm gonna burn it up, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,#8 The story of Saru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, it stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Like rotten eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you even smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I'm always the only one talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk now, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's practice talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, say something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, a bridal parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Something doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't let you shoot arrows \Nat a happy bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A happy bride? Yeah right! Big Sis is \Nbeing sent off to marry a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To marry a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So I gotta stop 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat it! Or I'll shoot you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm your horses. Tell me more about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We know a thing or two \Nabout beating monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A cloud right over the village. \NThat's the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,People call it Nokosaregumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,From way back in time, it's appeared  \N now and then to eat people up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One time, the villagers offered a bride  \N to keep it from eating the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it left without killing any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since, they've offered a bride  \N every time it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't offer one, it'll get mad \Nand eat up the whole village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a monster but it wants a human bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And a lot of them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis said it probably ate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never understand \Nhow a monster thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So your big sis was chosen this time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to help her. \NI don't want her to be eaten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can help you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy here has beaten up \Nlots of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He can beat it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Really? \N-But it's gonna cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't do it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not these. \NSomething worth money, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it in the river. I got lots of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You've got a deal then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Saru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Saru? Like a monkey? That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo is a funny name, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's not, it's a nice name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, say it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you over and over not to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're actually doing this \Nfor the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're using you to save themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any monster \Neating everybody up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. But you must leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, ease up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll beat that monster for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll solve all your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You? How will you defeat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If it eats people, it has to have \Na mouth and a belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll tear it apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,See? He's all ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots, it'll hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru's vision was surrounded  \N by a wall of evil flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The dark cloud was a part  \N of the devilish ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru was enclosed in a wall of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time ever,  \N he had completely lost his sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a centipede.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's humongous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah, I live on my own. \N-On your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis ain't my real sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived alone all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa and Mama died when I was real little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the mountain with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They said this wasn't my mountain  \N and drove me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hurt. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the boy  \N that lives in the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like a saru, a monkey.  \N What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't remember your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Saru. My name's Saru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watching her made me forget  \N about hunger and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama was the only one  \N who'd ever been kind to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was my mama once  \N sometime, in some place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mama, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Saru, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't got no time to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta avenge Big Sis. Ain't I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I never leave \Na job half done, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's beat it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but Hyakkimaru \Ncan't do anything when he's in that cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do it on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Has that cloud grown bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad. Centipedes get bigger \Nonce they molt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger? Even more than now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Isn't it supposed to go home \Nonce it has a bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mad about what we did to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Its weakness is sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If we lure it out of the cloud, \Nwe can beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I've got a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Saru. We'll exterminate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for my Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis... Big Sis...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Size doesn't mean a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to catch me with those hundred feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to you now, Saru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is for Big Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't burn in all that fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Melt away in the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it, after all we did, still nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He slashed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd he just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru had lost his sight  \N in the wall of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So he'd located the monster  \N by listening to the arrow hitting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:17:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, follow my voice! \NI'm on its head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he calling for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here, Hyakkimaru! \NIts eye is right next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a head on the tail, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Never been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Saru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru, is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You got your nose back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's what I promised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got lots of it around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The shiny ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I only had that little bit. \NThey're the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I'm still alive. \NYour name is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are y'all going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll live together in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm all alone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good for you, Saru. \N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, we need to think of \Na new name for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Saru's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, names are very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like you're really my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This sense is called smell, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say "Dororo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time he said my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's pretty nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow scatters in the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,piling up to form shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our footsteps admonish  \N indifference in such verbose ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:23:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As I peek into your fathomless eyes,  \N I lose my composure
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any hope  \N in the place I am heading to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I feign amusement and laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because this road is so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be there to shine the light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to playing at saying goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but I cried when I waved to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.19,0:23:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fiery woes fade... and fade...  \N until night falls upon us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew tomorrow would be so mundane,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.87,0:23:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have said that I wanted to live
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's futile but can't help dreaming  \N of a future... a future... you are to blame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nokosaregumo"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:17.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くっせぇ～…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,タマゴが腐った匂いみてぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきは平気なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そもそも匂いってわかんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちぇ～。おいらばっか喋ってさぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきだって喋れるようになったんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よし！おいらと話す練習だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:40.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さ！なんか話しかけてみてくれよ。あにき
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へぇー。花嫁行列だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なーんか変だな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！ちょ、ちょっと待てよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何すんだおめぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:23.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そりゃこっちだ！めでたい花嫁に矢なんか飛ばしやがって！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どういうつもりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:33.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,めでたくなんかねぇ！姉ちゃんはなぁ、\Nバケモンの嫁になりに行くんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモンの嫁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからおらぁが止めねぇと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:41.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,去ね！おめぇごと射んぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:45.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ待てって。よかったらその話聞かせてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらたち、バケモンにはちっとばかし縁があんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:02.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あそこだけ雲が浮いてら。あれがバケモン？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんが言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつぁ残され雲って呼ばれててな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:13.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昔っからこの辺りに現れちゃあ人を食っちまうんだってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:20.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だから、これ以上人を食わねぇでくれって、\Nあるときバケモンに嫁をやったそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしたらおとなしく帰ってったんだってよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:26.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それから、現れるたんびに嫁をやったそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:33.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もし嫁をやらねぇと、怒って村ごと食っちまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモンなのに人の嫁が欲しいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それも何人も
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんは全員食われちまっただろうって言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモンの考えることはよくわかんねぇなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:48.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,で、今回はおめぇの姉ちゃんが選ばれたんだな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:53.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらぁ姉ちゃんを助けてぇ。バケモンに食われちまうなんて嫌だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこでおいらたちの出番よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきはこれまでいろんなバケモンをやっつけてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんな雲イチコロって！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:05.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホントか！？\N-ただし、報酬はもらうけどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,タダ働きはしないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うめぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:19.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こういうんじゃなくてもっと金になりそうなモンだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こりゃ砂金だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:29.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,川で拾ったんだ。そんな石ならいっぺぇあんぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,欲しいだけやらぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:34.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ホントか？よし、取引成立。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら、どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:36.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらぁ、さるだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さる？それが名前か？変なの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろも変だー
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,変じゃない！いい名前だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いい名前って言えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくねぇから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:09.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:15.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前！あれだけ来ちゃいけねぇって！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんを助けに来たんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行けないよ、私は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もしかして…村のためか！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんなやつらほっとけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分らが助かるために姉ちゃんを差し出してよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:38.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:41.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あたしは自分から来たんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バケモンなんぞにみんなを食わせたくなくてね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前だってそうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:50.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらは姉ちゃんに死んでほしくねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いいからお逃げ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁ待ちなって！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:02.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お姉さん、おいらたちがそのバケモンやっつけてやるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうすりゃまるっと解決だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:08.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたは…？それに、やっつけるってどうやって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人を食うんならどっかに口とか腹とかあるはずさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そこをぶった斬るんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ほら、あにきも任せろって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちげぇよ…あいつが来たんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:29.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…なんだこりゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,い…今すぐ逃げとう…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,バカ！そんな大声出してると…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！あそこだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきってば！どうしたんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:05.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸の視界は一面炎に覆い尽くされていた。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:10.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,周囲に満ちる雲もまた、あやかしの一部だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,炎の壁に包まれた百鬼丸は、
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:18.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何も見えないという状態を初めて知ったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありゃ、ムカデだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:38.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とんでもねぇデカさだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！来るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はぁ…た、助かった…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここがさるの家か？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:45.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだぁ。おらぁ1人で住んでる\N1人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:48.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんはおらぁの姉ちゃんじゃねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらぁずっと1人で生きてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:58.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父ちゃんと母ちゃんは、おらぁがちっせぇ頃に病で死んじまった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも平気だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらぁにゃ、山があったから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,人は嫌ぇだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:15.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここはおらの山じゃなくなったってことや\Nおらを追い出すんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらぁに近寄んな！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ケガしてるんだろ？見せてごらん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:47.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたが山に住んでるって子かい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おさるみたいな顔やね！名前は？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:52.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,名前？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:57.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,自分の名前、忘れちまったのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さるだ。おらぁ、さるってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:11.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,不思議だったぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:18.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの姉ちゃんを見てるだけで、腹減ってんのも、さみぃのも気になんねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おらぁに優しくしてくれたのは、母ちゃんだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だからもしかして、
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:30.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの姉ちゃんはいつかどこかで\Nおらぁの母ちゃんだった人かと思いよったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…か…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さる…その…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,泣いてるヒマなんかぁねぇやろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:43.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんのカタキはおらぁが討たねぇと。そうだろ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:48.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ！おいらだって一度受けた仕事は\N最後まできっちりやるつもりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,一緒にあいつをやっつけんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぅ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ただ…な…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:04.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,理由はわかんねぇけど、あの雲の中じゃあにきは満足に動けねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらたちだけであいつをなんとかしなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？あの雲、前よりでっかくなってねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…なんだ？これ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こらぁやつの皮だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:26.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まじぃぞ、ムカデってぇのは脱皮すっとおっきくなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっきくって…あれよりもか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:34.10,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんでだよ！嫁をもらったらおとなしく帰るんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,昼間のことであいつも怒ってんのかもしんねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうするよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ…あいつの弱点は日光だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:48.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,からおてんと様の下に引きずり出せば倒せるはずだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それならおらぁにいい考えがあんぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やんぞ！さる！ムカデ退治だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ！姉ちゃんの弔い合戦だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:23.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん…姉ちゃんよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やーい！こっちだ！こっち！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハッ！でかけりゃいいってモンじゃねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:15.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その百本足でおいらを捕まえてみろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっちだ！こっち！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:40.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そろそろだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:44.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ってぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.03,0:15:53.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっぶねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ、さる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんのカタキだ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんだけの炎でも燃えないのかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:34.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:36.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも問題ねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのまま日の光にノビちまえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなぁ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:06.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちきしょう…こんだけやってもダメなのかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきが斬った！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:40.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何したんだ！？今！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,炎の壁で視界を塞がれた百鬼丸は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:49.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,矢の当たる音であやかしの位置を確かめていたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:17:59.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まじぃぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ！音だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうする気だ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:20.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！おいらの声のするところがムカデの頭だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もしかして…あいつを呼んでんのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！ここだ！おいらの横がこいつの目だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今度こそ終わりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,しっぽにも頭があんのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:41.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やったぁー！へへっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ、このとおり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:01.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:03.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:05.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さ、る…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだぁ…さるだぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:18.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,姉ちゃん、生きててよかった…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:24.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき？もしかして…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:32.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきの鼻が戻った！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:48.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁ！約束の報酬だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:49.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ。ありがとよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:53.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだよ、この石…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この辺りによーく落ちてんだー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらが欲しいのはこんな石じゃなくて砂金だって！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの金ぴかの石！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:05.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありゃあれだけだぁ。おんなじようなモンだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なっ…そ、そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:11.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたたちのおかげで、死なずに済んだよ。えっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:12.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありがとう。どろろさん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたら、これからどうすんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村で一緒に暮らそうかって。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あたしも1人だから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:29.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,-へぇ、よかったな！さる. \Nあぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:33.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうだ、名前！新しく考えないと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さるでいいよぉ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメ！名前は大事なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだかホントの姉ちゃんみてぇだな！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まぁいっか！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:58.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ど…ろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:02.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、これはな…匂いってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:07.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？今おいらのこと、どろろって…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:14.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,初めてだ、名前呼ばれたの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:19.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきぃ！待ってくれよぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:21.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらの名前いい名前だろ！？
